name: AI Upscaler Plugin 1.4
overview: AI-Powered Video Upscaling Plugin with Hardware Benchmarking
description: AI upscaling plugin with automated hardware benchmarking, intelligent fallback system, pre-processing cache, and advanced low-end hardware support. Features comprehensive performance testing, comparison view, TV remote optimization, and sidebar integration.

versions.changelog: v1.4.0 FINAL STABLE: Configuration crash fixed, automated hardware benchmarking system, intelligent fallback for low-end hardware (iGPUs, ARM, NAS), pre-processing cache for better performance, comparison view for quality testing, TV remote optimization (WebOS/Tizen), sidebar settings panel integration, comprehensive benchmark console with real-time testing, automatic model optimization based on hardware capabilities
